        <p>A depressed, whitish lesion on the buttocks.</p>
      </caption>
      <graphic xlink:href="ASM-29-153-g001"/>
    </fig>
    <p>What is your diagnosis?</p>
    <p>FOR THE ANSWER, VISIT:</p>
